                        <div class="q_bot" id="secInfo_281"><div class="secinfo">考点名称：<span class="secname">探究：环境因素对光合作用强度的影响</span></div><ul class="quesExtra"><li><div class="splitline"></div><div  class="notes"><P><STRONG>影响光合作用的因素及实践应用：<BR><BR></STRONG> 1．内部因素<BR> (1)与植物自身的遗传性有关，如阴生植物、阳生植物，<BR>如图所示：<IMG style="HEIGHT: 131px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; WIDTH: 211px" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/09/20131108/2013110811210013512526.png"> <BR>(2)植物叶片的叶龄、叶面积指数也会制约光合作用，<BR>如图所示：<IMG style="HEIGHT: 136px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle; WIDTH: 405px" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/09/20131108/2013110811210040021040.png"> <BR>2．外部因素 <BR>(1)单因子 <BR>
<TABLE style="BORDER-TOP-STYLE: solid; BORDER-LEFT-STYLE: solid; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; BORDER-BOTTOM-STYLE: solid; WORD-BREAK: break-all; BORDER-RIGHT-STYLE: solid" borderColor=infotext cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width=600 bgColor=highlighttext border=1>
